Backport of upstream commit 33ccdfb0a12690af5bb49bda2319ec0907fa7827
"Improve validation in HTTP parser (#8074)" for aiohttp 3.8.6.

Fixes CVE-2024-23829: HTTP request smuggling in the pure-Python parser
(GHSA-8qpw-xqxj-h4r2). Tightens validation of HTTP version, method,
header field-name, Content-Length, and HTTP status-code so the Python
parser rejects malformed inputs that the C/llhttp parser already
rejects.

Adapted to the 3.8.6 source layout (METHRE/VERSRE use .match() not
.fullmatch() in this version; minor surrounding-context drift in tests).

