  - aiohttp/web_request.py
  - tests/test_web_request.py

Files in the upstream commit deliberately NOT included (do not exist in 3.8.6):
  - aiohttp/_cookie_helpers.py (introduced after 3.8.x)
  - tests/test_cookie_helpers.py (introduced after 3.8.x)

